name: Tako of the Void
description:
A depiction of a takodachi, the mascot of Ninomae Ina'nis, a VTuber from the Hololive agency as part of Myth.

While this artwork was not planned by the VTubers fan coordination group, the character lore for Ina states that takodachis are creatures of the Void, presumably explaining the decision to place one right in the path of the Swarm's expansion.
